   <div>
    <h1 style="padding: 25px 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #000; padding-bottom: 10px;">发现自己醉后和老公单独待了一夜，她吓得慌忙逃跑，不是她老公不好而是……</h1>
   </div> 
   <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #999; padding-bottom: 23px; text-align: center;">
    <a href="account_duyueshiguang.shtml" class="accountlink">duyueshiguang</a> &nbsp; 2017-03-11
   </div> 
   <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #000;" id="content"> 
    <p><img style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0px auto;" data-type="gif" src="img.jsp?id=1200132&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fu3ECq93GjoDscbia58dROMeeCoJRTxbpd5mFQYnQvTBpOibj0P0xbsZWzszV38icalFPhK2RzsyEr0cRmE5yibYXYQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif" data-ratio="0.1761194029850746" data-w="670" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;"></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 24.381px; white-space: normal;"><img style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0px auto;" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="img.jsp?id=1200132&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHVCNCJx1llM9heN07xhoPlPR8R2B0fyUrEB3ej8eN6EUUQ19hpzV7Q32TzA71Wef56mVO8vRO0TUTyM3tz1Q2w%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-ratio="0.928125" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">娱乐城。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">包厢内。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">暗色的灯光有些让人恍如隔世，一股刺鼻的酒精味道环绕着安小暖身边。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖青涩的脸庞，无疑吸引着男人的征服欲，她穿着一条白色的裙子，虽然不暴露，可却让人想要“呵护”，男人淫荡的目光打量着，很明目张胆。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖闻着一股刺鼻的味道环绕着自己，恶心的想吐，她没有搭理他们，坐在那里紧张的打量着身边的几个男人，却见男人的手忽然附在了她的腿上，猥琐的脸慢慢的靠近着。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“姐姐，我去一下洗手间……”安小暖感觉身体异样，将喝完的酒杯丢给了木芸衫，踉踉跄跄的冲出了包厢。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“追！”沙发上的男人应声而立，朝着安小暖离开的方向而去。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">走廊上，响起了急促的脚步声和男人的低咒声，“废物，连个女人都抓不住，要你们有什么用。”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖一路小跑着，她觉得自己身体越来越热，她仔细回忆着刚刚包厢内发生的场景，是那杯酒的问题，木芸杉竟然给她下药，为了得到她的合同，竟然要把她丢给这些男人。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她眸色暗沉，握着自己手腕的手链，还好手链拿回来了，否则，真是想死的心都有了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">身后传来男人急促的脚步声和男人的咒骂声，“把她给我抓住了……”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她根本没有办法思考，打开了一扇黑色的大门，虚弱的她连关门的力气都没有。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“虎哥……那里好像是顾少爷的专属地方……”男人贴在虎哥耳边，指着自己不远处的地方。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">金色的雕花门虚掩着，门上的两条大金龙像是栩栩如生，亮着眼睛瞪着他们，让人浑身颤栗，而黑漆漆的里面看不出来什么。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“走！”虎哥听完男人的话，脸色瞬间变了，恶狠狠地盯了几分钟那扇微掩盖的大门，手心握成了拳头。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">这西城都是顾家的天下，谁敢得罪了顾少爷，那就是再跟阎王作对。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">套房内，黑暗的环境下，窗口被那密不透风的窗帘掩盖的死死地，完全不透一点光。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">沙发上，男人欣长的身躯埋在那里，黑眸紧紧地闭着，整个人像是蕴藏在黑暗中的死神一样，高挺的鼻梁，薄情的嘴唇，让人身心畏惧。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">陌生的气息让顾西城的黑眸缓缓张开，忽然有瞬间变了冷意，他渐渐地从沙发上坐起，黑隼的眸光在看到门口的黑影时，完美的唇角往上扬了扬。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“这里……也是你想来就来的地方？”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">他的步子渐渐落在安小暖面前，一股按压下来的气势已经让安小暖完全没有办法摆脱。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">他身上有着淡淡的味道，很清凉。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖像是抓住了什么救命稻草，拉着男人的手，直接落进了他的怀里。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“救我……”她神志不清，只是觉得男人的手臂很凉，很舒服。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">黑暗中，一股奶香味充斥着顾西城的鼻尖，而身上暖炉一般的女人像是一个八爪鱼一样挂在了自己身上，冲击着他引以为傲的自制力。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">女人的头埋在男人的肩膀处，她整个人已经没有力气，全身冒火难受极了，额头上的刘海已经被汗水沾湿了，粘在上面，而唇瓣微微的张着呼着气。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“滚！”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">男人黑眸闪现着怒意，嘴里轻吐着的话，冲击着安小暖的心脏。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“我……难受……”她可怜兮兮的埋在男人的肩膀处，眼泪哗哗的往下掉。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">温热的眼泪正巧一滴一滴的落在男人的脖子处，男人冰凉的身体微微一僵。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">而后，女人攀岩着男人的手臂开始慢慢松了，整个人往后倒去。男人眼疾手快的拉住了女人逐渐落下来的手臂，将她忘怀中一带，闻着她身上的味道，忽然有一刹那恍惚。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“不后悔吗？”男人低沉的嗓音在安小暖耳边响起，带着诱惑。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">忽然，不等女人反应，他低着头狠狠地吻住了女人微张的粉唇，甜美的滋味让人上瘾。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">男人冰凉的唇瓣贴着女人炽热的嘴唇，安小暖似乎像是被全身注入了生命一样，重获新生。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖青涩的吻技，显得非常生疏。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“你会死，也不介意吗？”他以为简单的一个吻就会让他放手，可谁知道青涩的吻一沾上，就根本一点喊停止的机会。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“我……难受……”女人的声音，无疑是催化剂，一点一点击溃着男人的心房。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城低头，再一次吻住了那张喋喋不休的嘴。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">两具年轻的身体紧紧的纠缠着，在密不透风的室内，响起了一阵涟漪。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">跳跃的阳光，透着密不可分的窗帘，撒来了第一道光芒，落在地板上，呈现着一道完美的弧线。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一室的混乱，空气中带着奢靡的味道。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">清晨，细碎的微风吹拂着窗帘，响起了一阵荡漾。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“好疼……”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">床上，女人一身轻呼，缓缓地睁开了沉重的双眸，她全身像是被碾压过了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她的手轻轻垂着自己的脑袋，在看到陌生的环境，瞪着眼睛整个人都蒙圈了，而后一下子唰的从床上坐起，看到自己全身触目惊心的痕迹，眸色暗沉。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她被人睡了？</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">被人睡了？巨大的信息量从她脑海中像是盛开的烟火一样炸开。昨天喝了木芸衫给她的酒，全身发热？然后她就跑进了这里？再然后……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">想到昨晚的种种，她的脸像是红苹果一样刷刷的红透了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">不过之后，她的思绪开始游离，该不会是个老头，秃顶……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">于是乎，她闭着眼睛转身，朝着男人的脸摸去……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">头发还挺长，不是秃头，脸上质感还不错，应该也不是老头。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她缓缓睁开眼睛，忽然一张沉睡着的面孔在她面前渐渐清晰，她的手僵持在空中，心脏久久不能平静。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城？安小暖第一眼就认出了这个男人，一个月前一场没有新郎的婚礼，让她在西城成为了轰动人物。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">而现在躺在床上的男人竟然是他，她的丈夫，这狗血的剧情还能再狗血一点吗？</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">这要是被他知道，岂不是会戳穿她的身份？不行，得赶紧走，趁他还没醒？璀璨的水晶手链遗落在床沿，她一把将它握在手里。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她匆匆的下床，看着地上的内衣裤，手忙脚乱的穿着，而看着一侧被男人撕碎的裙子，惊慌失措的小心脏扑通扑通的跳动着，顺手抓过男人的衬衫，直接套在了身上，还好他的衬衫很长，一直遮挡住了她的腿，一边穿着地上的鞋子，一边手指慌乱的扣着扣子，冲出门外。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">床上的男人缓缓睁开了眼睛，他犀利的黑眸扫了一圈床头，凌乱的枕头摆放在他身侧，昨夜的女人像是一个梦境一般，一沾上如同是罂粟花一样可以让人瞬间上瘾，枕头上，似乎还能闻到她身上淡淡的奶香味。他锐利的双眸扫了一圈周围，却不见女人的身影。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一向自制力极好的他，怎么会……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">他的视线不经意的落在在床单上的那抹猩红，凌乱的床单像是经历了巨大的磨难，如同是一个被卷成椭圆形的大蛋糕。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">昨夜的记忆蜂拥而至，如同是一个放映机一样在脑海中穿梭，只是她的模样与暗黑重叠，这一切恍如梦境……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">他越想心情越烦躁，胸口像是被一块巨石堵住了一样，异常的情绪扰的男人心绪不宁，随即一脚踢开脚上的薄被，从床上起来，阴鸷的目光扫过在灰色地毯上，一件被撕碎的连衣裙被遗落在地上。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">他伸手将地上的裙子捡起，这衣服看起来为什么这么眼熟？</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">叩叩叩。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">房门被人敲响，木森恭敬的拿着一套西装进来，看着面前的男人正注视着手里的衣服，“哥，你的衣服。”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城直接将他无视，将手里的衣服丢了过去，然后将他手上的西装勾了过来，迈着大步朝着浴室而去。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">半个小时后。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">男人穿着一身阿玛尼限量版西服套装，脚踩着一双意大利纯手工皮鞋从浴室里面出来。幽冷的脸上没有多余的表情，扫过呆愣在原地的木森，冷冷的说道，“还有事？”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“呃……哥，那个……昨晚那个女人没事……”木森一个字一个字从嘴里吐出来，眼睛盯着顾西城的表情渐渐的变化，腿都有些抖了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“人呢？”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">鲜有人知，在商界只手遮天，俊美多金的顾少爷会身中蛊毒，碰过的女人会立刻休克，所以也导致了他对女人也提不上兴趣，更别说是跟他一起过夜。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城身形微怔，犹如突入冰窖中，忽然犹如把他拉向了光明，一双淡漠的双眸充斥着猩红，眼睛死死地盯着木森手里的衣服。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“那个……跑了。”木森在触及到顾西城的眼神时，一时间也不知道怎么去运用语言，为自己捏了一把汗。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“找！挖地三尺也给我找出来。”顾西城双眸闪过犀利，扫过对面的男人。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“把娱乐城所有的摄像头都给我调出来。”忽然，顾西城开口道，紧接着迈着大步，朝着大门而去。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">狭窄的阁楼安板上，堆满了一地的衣服。一条白色的男士衬衫夹杂在地上的一堆衣服中，显得非常起眼。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">耳畔，忽然闪过男人低沉的嗓音，“你会死也不介意吗？”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一想到这句话，她整个人抖了抖，心脏开始扑通扑通的乱跳。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她摸着乱跳的心口，眼神迷离的盯着地上的衬衫，此时白色衬衫上已经沾上了她细碎的脚印。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城，真是阴魂不散。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她晃了晃脑袋，不让这莫名的情绪干扰她的想法。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">不过，这衬衫，应该丢在哪里才不会被发现呢？她的眉头皱成了一个大大的川字，长长的呼了一口气。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">俗话说，最危险的地方就是最安全的地方，倒不如就藏在阁楼吧。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">废掉的脑细胞已经让安小暖整个人都不好了，她一把抓起地上的衬衫，直接扭成了一团，塞进了衣柜。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">半个小时后。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">叩叩叩。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一道浑厚的嗓音从门口传来，“夫人，少爷今天要回来了，您赶紧下来，别让少爷等急了！”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖愣住原地，几百年不来别墅的人，他竟然来了？真的是阴魂不散。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“好……”反应过来后，安小暖扬起她招牌式的笑容，刷的一下打开了门。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾管家看着面前的安小暖，此刻她蓬乱的头发如一个鸡窝，身上穿着一条宽松的睡袍，赤着脚的站在安板上，问难的说道，“夫人，您就这样下去？”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖安讷的低着头，看了一眼自己的穿着，好像是有哪里不对劲！</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“哦！您等我一下。”安小暖垫着小脚丫，从门口鞋柜子拿了一双拖鞋，套在了脚上。然后理了理自己蓬乱的头发。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“走吧！”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一张大型的长方形欧式餐桌上，摆满了各式各样的食物，安小暖从旋转楼梯上下来，就闻到了烧鸡的味道，口水都要流下来了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“好饿……”她在心里呐喊了一声，直接冲到了餐桌前，看着面前的巧克力松露，煎鹅肝蛋卷等让她垂涎欲滴的食物。松露，鹅肝这些可都是法式顶级食材啊，看着满桌的钱，安小暖的心都在痛啊。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她直接推开欧式座椅，屁股还没有落地，就听着身后的几个女佣在一旁窃窃私语。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“你看她，土包子就是土包子，怎么装都成不了凤凰。”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“切，还以为自己嫁入豪门了，谁知道我们少爷几百年都不会老宅。”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“……”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">不时，从后面传来了各种讽刺的话，简直已经把安小暖贬的一文不值。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">就在这个时候，顾总管从里侧冲了出来，身后跟着女佣和随从们，面色紧张不安。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“少爷来了，还不赶紧去迎接……”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">别墅外。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“吱……”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一辆黑色的劳斯劳斯停在别墅外，车轮与地面做着亲密的碰触，流线型的车身在雨下冲刷的更加锃亮。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">司机从驾驶座跑出来，撑了一把黑色的伞着急的走到后座，打开了车门。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一条黑色的地毯铺在车外，长长的黑色地毯通往别墅里侧。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“少爷！”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">保镖三三两两的站在雨里，齐声喊了一声，等待着顾西城现身。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">男人修长的腿跨进安小暖的范围内，漆黑色的皮鞋落入安小暖的眼中，一股锐不可当的气势如冲破云霄，压迫着坐在凳子上的安小暖。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城阴鸷的眼神触及脚边的安小暖，“这是怎么回事？随随便便的人都能上餐桌了？”</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">闻言，安小暖扯了扯自己低垂的嘴角。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">随随便便的人？说的是她？</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“少爷，这是夫人，安小暖！”顾管家朝着顾西城看去的方向解释道。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">顾西城这才注意到餐桌前的女人，她穿着一条宽松的睡衣，那款式明显都不知道淘汰了多久，包裹着瘦弱的身材像是一个发育不良的小学生，此刻她坐在餐桌上，局促不安。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">这是他第一次见她，不觉某处有些熟悉的味道。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖忽然仰头，光照下，男人近乎完美的的脸，帅气鲜明的棱角如上帝宠爱的娇儿，浑然天成的霸气给人一种无形的压力，周围弥漫着刺骨的气息，她脑海中忽然飘过昨夜的画面，脸一下子有些红透，她狠狠地掐了一下自己的腿，在心底直接把自己鄙视了一番。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖，能不能有点出息。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她歪着头，眼睛一直盯着墙边的青瓷色花瓶，心里思忖着。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">看顾西城的样子，应该不知道昨晚的人是她吧。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">男人的视线落在女人面前的食物上，已经烧糊的鸡蛋和一杯牛奶，是她的晚餐。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“我顾家的女人就吃这种食物，穿这种破旧的衣服？从今天开始，要是再让我看见这种垃圾出现在顾家，所有人给我滚蛋。”男人低沉的嗓音回荡在这个别墅。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">闻言，女佣们纷纷低着头，颤抖的双腿因为男人的声音而变得慌乱不安，周围似乎连大口呼吸都不敢。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖盯着男人的脸，心中涌现出一丝异常，这是第一次有人关心她。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“你们最好记住这是谁的地盘！”说完，顾西城挎着大步而去。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">客厅内，安小暖一脸崇拜的望着男人离去的背影，哇塞，顾西城还挺帅的。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">而身侧的女佣默认的垂头，安小暖见状，嗤嗤一笑。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“夫人，我带您去换一身，顺便洗个澡吧！”女佣恭敬的对着发愣的安小暖说道，似乎一脸真诚，没有了以往的刁难。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖暗自忖度，果然顾西城的话，很受用。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">十分钟后。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">巨型的室内温泉池内，玫瑰花漂浮在池水之上，香气怡人的环境内，水中女人冥神的闭着眼睛，背靠在一块岩石上。萦绕在女人身边的白色烟雾，像是给女人披了一件外衣。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">女人肌肤雪白通透，如池内的牛奶般光滑丝质，原本黑漆漆的小脸，此时像是脱了皮的鸡蛋，恢复了原本的白净。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安静的温泉池内，只听着水流缓缓流淌的水声，滴答滴答的继续着它的工作。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖竖着耳朵，仔细的搜寻着周围的脚步声……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她胡乱的拍着池内的池水，水花四溅，许久，没有得到回应，一双睿智的眼睛缓缓睁开，唇角勾着一抹鄙夷。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖勾了勾岸上的衣服，往身上一披，一下子从池内站起，修长的腿带走了一些水花，湿漉漉的小脚直接落在安板上。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">衣服的上部被剪刀剪开，穿了跟没穿无两样，她擎着一抹复杂的笑容，为了难为她，真是无时无刻让她们煞费苦心啊，嘴角的冷笑溢满全脸，但是很快就掩盖好了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她撤掉身上多余的纽扣，只扭了几颗，简单的将衣服扭成一团，把长款衣服折叠翻上，在胸部处绑了一个蝴蝶结，弯腰捡起地上的裤子，三下两下的往身上套上。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">落地镜前，女人湿漉漉的头发被胡乱的绑着，虽说整个衣服有些凌乱，但也算挡住了外露的春光。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">想让我出丑，也不看看我是谁。她哼着小歌，扭着头蹦蹦跳跳的离开。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">身后，某扇如岩石的大门缓缓而开，男人穿着白色的浴袍，一双阴眸死死的盯着远去的女人。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">他像是看到了猎物一样，嘴角勾着笑意……有趣。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">阁楼。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">阁楼一角，精致的雕花安板上随处可见的杂物堆满了一地，一张小床摆放在那里占据了一壁江山。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">微风从外迎来，一股沁人心脾的味道席卷安小暖的鼻尖。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">安小暖趴在小床上，翘着她的小腿，正在玩着她从管家那里要来的笔记本上，她的手自在键盘上快速的敲击着，跳跃着如同在弹奏着音符，神情专注着。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">屏幕上，各式各样的字符像是滚动的屏幕一样刷刷刷的在眼前飞逝而过……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">寂静的夜晚，只听着女人打着键盘的声音此起彼伏的从远处而来。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">女人穿着比较旧的睡衣款式，白色的睡衣有些褶皱，她高高挽起的头发，现已经松垮垮的遗落在肩膀上。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她趴在硬邦邦的安板床上，全身骨头都被印床板咯的疼。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">“终于弄完了……”安小暖按下最后的发送键，终于这款游戏算是做完了。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">她翻了一个身，咯吱咯吱想的小床显然有些承受不住她的重力，开始晃动起来。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一座打造的精致的小洋房坐落在别墅的内侧，雕花的石板门像是一个守卫的将领，将小洋房紧紧地包围着。</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">一道嘶吼般的叫声从小洋房内传来……</span></p>
    <p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <table data-sort="sortDisabled" width="670">
     <tbody style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
